{"tid":949134,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕動漫台緣份計劃意見及人口調查　","createTime":"2018-12-20T14:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T15:04:46.000Z","uid":176045,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad543243509d3146cf64d7275ac745836cf53b4","tid":949134,"uid":176045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"<del>在動漫台尋求邂逅是否搞錯了什麼?</del><br />\n<br />\n大家好，小弟有意係LIHKG搞只屬於動漫台既緣份計劃，比大家認識興趣相近既異性或同性啦。<br />\n想大家花小小時間填份問卷比意見，睇下可唔可行，多唔多人參與。如果過半數反對我自己收皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外，仲想做個人口調查，統計大家瀏覽動漫台既習慣。個人對動漫台既生態圈好有興趣，希望兩星期內整到個報告比大家。<br />\n歡迎大家提出唔同既意見<del>/狠評</del>，感謝各位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問卷調查Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/e6Plh03iiQCCX5p73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2Fe6Plh03iiQCCX5p73&d=fuxLroCnnWUwqjsasrgK4NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b906dd54\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/e6Plh03iiQCCX5p73</a><br />\n<br />\nReference: <br />\n好宅之人 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/veryotaku\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fveryotaku&d=fuxLroCnnWUwqjsasrgK4NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9d65f07b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/veryotaku</a><br />\n緣份配對計劃 <a href=\"https://matchup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatchup.hk&d=fuxLroCnnWUwqjsasrgK4NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e1658ee7\" target=\"_blank\">https://matchup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"2c96add47ebe1dbc0502725493e7c3f5118bdbbd","tid":949134,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"我有聲優女朋友 不用了"},{"pid":"93c1dc855ec434a265678037747ee22e5f1d4070","tid":949134,"uid":31374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"我希望識到個鐘意刀劍既男朋友"},{"pid":"549c0c8100a252ee3d67cd098c9cc5a186354e10","tid":949134,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0